{"tid":755363,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人諗住報名做2020東京奧運會義工？","createTime":"2018-07-25T07:08:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-19T03:50:12.000Z","uid":185469,"like":10,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"a9b4022b70b6720623301f93d334954ef48e8334","tid":755363,"uid":185469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T07:08:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tokyo2020.org/en/special/volunteer/activity/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftokyo2020.org%2Fen%2Fspecial%2Fvolunteer%2Factivity%2F&d=FWxduykNtOOU8L%2FspW3vaBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=e367ee4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://tokyo2020.org/en/special/volunteer/activity/</a><br />\n<br />\n今次會請十一萬人，只要到時年過18歲就可以報名，年紀冇上限<br />\n一做要起碼做十日，不過唔包住宿要自己搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然要倒貼，但人生有得近距離睇奧運會點搞都幾過癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有冇人諗住報名？好似9月開始"},{"pid":"2099b3f2595b13b322d65c66e536b55417ea66de","tid":755363,"uid":50779,"like":40,"dislike":5,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T07:40:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9a53ce36dde45541c3331d29ed7d6685a5812c55","tid":755363,"uid":28,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T07:40:50.000Z","msg":"會報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢10日duty仲要唔一定連續10日on duty，可以隔日先去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當放假一部份玩下"},{"pid":"55751b9bdfb1777312f829d0ba977d9d373bb19a","tid":755363,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":28,"score":-28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T07:41:50.000Z","msg":"唉差一年先得"},{"pid":"c0da3dc04d11237b00e7ffb4457b4672b7952d23","tid":755363,"uid":85478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T13:57:00.000Z","msg":"有冇同路人有興趣開個gp 大家一齊keep mon 住最新消息"},{"pid":"9c93b1b4f344381dbe8d7e474bb8cd6a312031b7","tid":755363,"uid":82640,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T14:18:31.000Z","msg":"冇